description: Take a ride on a some of the largest stern steerer iceboats (35-40ft) around.  "Rainbow" (2nd)is over 100 years old and now presides on White Bear Lake.  "Country Woman" is a hot ride...and really fast!  This may have been the last ride on these great boats until the next season.
